viewData.name: PhiNesse Brush Eye Shader Brush 8
viewData.short_description: A soft and dense brush to shade or blend eye shadow. This brush has a rounded edge with smooth, firm, fine fibres. It can be used to build and press intense colour on the lid. PhiAcademy professional brushes are hand-sculpted and assembled using the finest quality materials.┬á
